<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1438,1595,1944]" pageId="10" pageNumber="209">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,306,1812,1836]" pageId="10" pageNumber="209">Notes:—</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Martinez-Gordillo, M. &amp; Jimenez, J. &amp; Cruz, R. &amp; Juarez, E. &amp; Garcia, R. &amp; Cervantes, A. &amp; Mejia, R." box="[307,658,1812,1837]" pageId="10" pageNumber="209" pagination="155 - 281" refId="ref20642" refString="Martinez-Gordillo, M., Jimenez, J., Cruz, R., Juarez, E., Garcia, R., Cervantes, A. &amp; Mejia, R. (2002) Los generos de la familia Euphorbiaceae en Mexico. Anales del Instituto de Biologia de la Universidad Nacional Autonoma de Mexico 73 (2): 155 - 281." type="journal article" year="2002">
Martínez-Gordillo 
<emphasis box="[519,576,1812,1837]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="209">et al.</emphasis>
(2002)
</bibRefCitation>
reported this species in 
<collectingCountry box="[932,1056,1812,1837]" name="Guatemala" pageId="10" pageNumber="209">Guatemala</collectingCountry>
, although 
<bibRefCitation author="Standley, P. C. &amp; Steyermark, J. A." pageId="10" pageNumber="209" pagination="1 - 440" refId="ref22982" refString="Standley, P. C. &amp; Steyermark, J. A. (1949) Flora of Guatemala. Fieldiana, Botany 24 (6): 1 - 440." type="journal article" year="1949">Standley &amp; Steyermark (1949)</bibRefCitation>
did not mention it in their Flora of 
<collectingCountry box="[657,788,1847,1872]" name="Guatemala" pageId="10" pageNumber="209">Guatemala</collectingCountry>
. The species has often been misidentified as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Muller Argoviensis" authorityYear="1865" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Acalypha" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="209" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="schlechtendaliana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="209">Acalypha schlechtendaliana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. After studying the 
<typeStatus box="[597,647,1884,1908]" pageId="10" pageNumber="209">type</typeStatus>
collections of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lundell" authorityYear="1976" box="[821,1125,1884,1909]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Acalypha" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="209" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tamaulipasensis">
<emphasis box="[821,1125,1884,1909]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="209">Acalypha tamaulipasensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, we did not find sufficient differences to distinguish it from 
<emphasis box="[524,658,1919,1944]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="209">
<taxonomicName authorityName="S. Watson" authorityYear="1891" box="[524,654,1919,1944]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Acalypha" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="209" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longipes">A. longipes</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
